headline: Upwork: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: UPWK) on Monday reported net income of $37.7 million in its first quarter. The Palo Alto, California-based company said it had net income of 27 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were 34 cents per share.
